{"tid":2021042,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"都是他爹媽的錯 - 李純恩","createTime":"2020-05-17T13:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T13:12:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67cf4c0db3d25150ee9f8ac39ca7dbb322619e39","tid":2021042,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9/daily/article/20200517/20919269/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200517%2F20919269%2F&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=8cafb8ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200517%2F20919269%2F&h=2ab8c040\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9/daily/article/20200517/20919269/</a><br />\n<br />\n都是他爹媽的錯 - 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200517/large/1589612395_7355.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200517%2Flarge%2F1589612395_7355.jpg&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=b661d8cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200517/large/1589612395_7355.jpg</a><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n一個中國男中音歌唱家，移民到了德國，胸懷祖國──當然是中國──在網上招徠中國學生，教歌唱技巧，如何運氣，如何運腔，頭頭是道。因為胸懷祖國，在疫情爆發之時，還特地作曲，引吭高歌，為武漢打氣，大概覺得自己號召力不夠，找來世界三大男高音之一的卡羅雷斯助陣，一起在鏡頭前高叫「加油」，愛國情操，令人感動。<br />\n<br />\n但就是這麼一位愛國男中音，卻被網站「抖音」三次封號，差點消失。被封號的原因，不是他歌藝不行，也沒說他有支持。。。。。。。。。。。。張臉長得像誰不好，偏偏有八成長得像習大大。一張臉於是給熱愛習大大的網民舉報，說他「形像違規」。結果一次又一次封掉賬號。<br />\n<br />\n這件事情絕對說明了為人父母的重大責任，除了不可以為兒子改錯。。。。。。。。。。貌堂堂」就有運行，有時真的需要獐頭鼠目才能避災難。<br />\n<br />\n可見這位愛國男中音的無辜，就是遇到了一對不會生的父母，好生不生，把他生成如今這個尷尬模樣，弄得麻煩從天降。他又偏偏移民去了馬克思的家鄉，人家那裏不流。。。。。。。。。。。。下五除二，將一張「習近平臉」改裝成南韓前總統李明博，從「相貌堂堂」降到「獐頭鼠目」，便可在「抖音」上東山再起，除了「在那遙遠的地方有個好姑娘」，還可以高歌《阿里郎》，必定麻煩盡去，學生湧現，勢如破竹。<br />\n<br />\n這位中國男中音的遭遇，還說明了一個道理，那就是孩子永遠沒有錯，世上只有爹媽錯。爹媽錯，兒子滿盤皆落索。 <br />\n<br />\n李純恩<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"36c6a379d2be06d041f975937c581c058019aa6c","tid":2021042,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:08:26.000Z","msg":"【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】：<br />\n<a href=\"http://legcopetition.wixsite.com/form\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flegcopetition.wixsite.com%2Fform&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=bab71aaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">legcopetition.wixsite.com/form</a>"},{"pid":"57326b1bc75f65546ff461201f5f35a76cc3c989","tid":2021042,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:08:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">他媽爹順少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f22ff73f48a9512c6fd99eeefc0cb4103c30166d","tid":2021042,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}